title: Binky Felstead pregnant with Josh 'JP' Paterson's baby - but they're still not officially a couple
text:
Binky Felstead, Alexandra Felstead, JP Patterson, Josh Patterson (Photo: WENN) Share Get celebs   Thank you for subscribing!   
Binky Felstead is pregnant with her first baby, with her Made In Chelsea costar Josh ‘JP’ Paterson. 
But the couple aren’t actually still together - and trying to work out their relationship. 
The reality TV stars announced the happy news in Hello! magazine, saying: "It’s obviously been a huge shock to both of us. 
“This is a new start and a new chapter in our lives. I want to be a little family, to be honest. But I'm going to be ok either way. 
“Whatever happens, this baby is not going to be affected. And I know Josh will be part of the baby’s life whether we are together or not. We are a unit now." Like us on Facebook
